description: ITEQ seeks investment results that generally correlate (before fees and expenses) to the total return performance of the BlueStar Israel Global Technology Index. ITEQ tracks a portfolio of Israeli technology companies that are at the forefront of most technologically disruptive industries, including cyber security, big data hardware and analytics, autonomous driver assistance and safety, clean energy, biotechnology and medical devices.
name: Amplify BlueStar Israel Technology ETF
